## Datetime Stamp Field

A datetime field that captures a precise timestamp

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import DatetimeStampField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/datetime-stamp';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field recordedAt = contains(DatetimeStampField);
}
```
